# Armis Collectors – Product Listing and Aging View  
## Operational Visibility Overview

This Splunk view provides centralized visibility into all deployed Armis Collectors, combining lifecycle tracking, configuration validation, network posture review, and proxy compliance into a single operational dashboard.

---

## 1️⃣ Collector Inventory & Lifecycle Monitoring

The view displays:

- Total number of collectors
- Identification of:
  - Oldest collector
  - Newest collector
- Detailed aging metrics (years / months / days / minutes)
- Per-collector metadata:
  - Creation date
  - Last seen timestamp
  - System vendor
  - Product serial number
  - MAC address
  - IP address
  - Subnet
  - Default gateway

### Operational Value
- Identifies aging collectors
- Detects collectors that may no longer be reporting
- Supports lifecycle management planning
- Provides authoritative inventory validation

---

## 2️⃣ Network Configuration Visibility

The dashboard surfaces configuration conditions such as:

- Collectors using Microsoft APIPA addresses (169.254.x.x)
- Collectors with blank default gateways
- Collectors configured with:
  - Single DNS entries
  - Specific DNS (e.g., 8.8.8.8)
  - NTP set to time.cloudflare.com
- Percentage-based distribution of DNS and NTP configurations

### Operational Value
- Detects network misconfiguration
- Highlights non-standard DNS/NTP settings
- Supports configuration standard enforcement
- Reduces risk of time synchronization or resolution issues

---

## 3️⃣ Proxy Configuration & Egress Control

The view provides visibility into:

- Number of collectors using the approved enterprise proxy
- Percentage using the approved proxy
- Percentage using a proxy that is not approved
- Count of collectors violating proxy standards

### Operational Value
- Validates outbound inspection enforcement
- Detects unauthorized egress configurations
- Supports network security governance

---

## 4️⃣ Operational Status Distribution

Collector status categories displayed:

- Active
- Collector Received
- Inactive
- In Shipping

### Operational Value
- Identifies non-reporting systems
- Highlights deployment pipeline state
- Supports readiness tracking

---

## 5️⃣ Detailed Collector Listing

The detailed table provides:

- Collector ID
- Hostname
- Vendor
- Serial number
- MAC address
- IP address
- Subnet
- Default gateway
- DNS servers
- NTP servers
- Exact calculated age

### Operational Value
- Enables rapid troubleshooting
- Supports hardware traceability
- Provides configuration verification at the individual system level
